  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 0ce21ed652be13542acd56ce31de69b5, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "And I didn\u2019t want to be like a suppressive male, so I was like
    \u2018Yeah, Tammy! I think you\u2019ll be great for presenting the bonfire!\u2019
    I really hope she gets the spot, it would be so awesome to have a La-tinks section
    leader for once in our very Moldovan company\u2019s lifetime\u2026 But then I
    was like snooping through Emma\u2019s social media, and it turned out, she\u2019d
    actually liked this one single robophobic tweet\u2026 Are chilli dogs appropriate
    for a BBQ?"
